*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
* Authorization Object: ZANM_AUTH
* Description: Anomaly Detective authorization object
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
* Fields:
*   ACTVT - Activity
*     01 = Create
*     02 = Change
*     03 = Display
*     16 = Execute
*   BUKRS - Company Code
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*

* Note: This file documents the authorization object definition.
* In SAP, create via SU21 or ADT with the following specification:

* Authorization Object : ZANM_AUTH
* Text                 : Anomaly Detective Authorization
* Object Class         : ZANM (create custom class if needed)
*
* Fields:
*   Field Name : ACTVT
*   Data Element: ACTIV_AUTH
*   Permitted Activities: 01, 02, 03, 16
*
*   Field Name : BUKRS
*   Data Element: BUKRS
*   All values permitted

* Transport: Include in workbench transport request
